# Privacy Policy for mynt

mynt is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by our app.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect your email address only for the purpose of authentication or communication. No other personal data, location, media, or device information is collected.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your email address to:

Enable secure sign-in and authentication

Communicate with you for support or updates

We do not use your data for advertising, analytics, or any third-party sharing.

3. Data Retention
We retain your email information only for as long as necessary to provide services. Once you delete your account or stop using the app, your data is removed.

4. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
The app is designed for users of all age groups. It does not target children under the age of 13 directly and does not knowingly collect data from them.

5. Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or misuse.

